C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-day-workweek-colorado-golden-police-reduction-hours-employment-pay-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20first%20US%20moon%20lander%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years%20launched%20with%20human%20remains%20on%20board%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20space%20burials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20shows%20ULA's%20Vulcan%20Centaur%20rocket%20taking%20off%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20blast%20of%20energy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659bd5871c5c7b8c9a0eb3be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAstrobotic's%20Peregrine%20lander%20launched%20toward%20the%20moon%20on%20Monday%2C%20January%208%2C%20from%20Cape%20Canaveral%20Space%20Force%20Station%20in%20Florida.%3Cp%3EAstrobotic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20US%20spacecraft%20carrying%20human%20remains%20launched%20on%20Monday%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeregrine%20could%20become%20the%20first%20US%20mission%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years%20to%20complete%20a%20touchdown.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20successful%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20the%20first%20private%20mission%20to%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20spacecraft%20carrying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-falcon-heavy-launch-cremated-remains-celestis-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuman%20remains%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20on%20Monday%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20become%20the%20first%20private%20mission%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20succeeds%2C%20Peregrine%20will%20also%20be%20the%20first%20US%20mission%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years%20to%20complete%20a%20lunar%20touchdown%20and%20could%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20commercial%20space%20services%2C%20such%20as%20lunar%20burials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20moment%20we've%20been%20waiting%20for%2016%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Thornton%2C%20CEO%20of%20Astrobiotic%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20lander%2C%20said%20after%20the%20launch.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20on%20our%20way%20to%20the%20moon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vulcan%20Centaur%20rocket%2C%20developed%20by%20United%20Launch%20Alliance%2C%20blasted%20off%20from%20Cape%20Canaveral%20Space%20Force%20Station%20in%20Florida%20at%20around%202%20a.m.%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20the%20Peregrine%20spacecraft%20separated%20from%20the%20rocket%20and%20began%20its%20journey%20to%20the%20lunar%20surface%2C%20where%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20land%20on%20February%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commercial%20mission%20is%20carrying%20more%20than%2020%20payloads%2C%20including%20five%20scientific%20missions%20from%20NASA%20and%20some%20more%20unconventional%20items%20like%20human%20DNA%20and%20cremated%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20shows%20the%20Astrobotic%20lander%20positioned%20inside%20the%20ULA%20rocket.%20The%20rocket%20is%20halfway%20opened%2C%20revealing%20the%20lander.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659bd6011c5c7b8c9a0eb3c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Peregrine%20lander%20aboard%20the%20Centaur%20Vulcan%20rocket%20ahead%20of%20launch.%3Cp%3EAstrobotic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20capsules%20on%20board%20the%20lander%20are%20part%20of%20a%20memorial%20service%20offered%20by%20private%20companies%20Celestis%20and%20Elysium%20Space.%20Both%20offer%20to%20take%20ashes%20to%20space%2C%20while%20Celestis%20will%20also%20bring%20human%20DNA%20from%20a%20mouth%20swab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelestis%20had%20two%20payloads%20on%20the%20launch%3A%20one%20aboard%20the%20United%20Launch%20Alliance%20Vulcan%20rocket%20that%20sent%20the%20lander%20to%20space%2C%20and%20one%20aboard%20the%20Peregrine%20lander%20heading%20to%20the%20moon%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20remains%20and%20DNA%20brought%20on%20the%20rocket%20include%20Gene%20Roddenberry%2C%20Star%20Trek's%20creator%2C%20and%20actors%20who%20played%20in%20the%20show%2C%20including%20Roddenberry's%20wife%20Majel%20Barrett%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F01%2F08%2Fscience%2Fvulcan-rocket-launch-moon.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20capsule%20contains%20the%20hair%20of%20George%20Washington%2C%20Dwight%20Eisenhower%2C%20and%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20those%20whose%20DNA%20and%20ashes%20are%20heading%20to%20the%20moon%20aboard%20Peregrine%2C%20one%20name%20stands%20out%20%E2%80%94%20Arthur%20C%20Clarke%2C%20famed%20science-fiction%20writer%20who%20co-wrote%20the%20script%20for%202001%3A%20A%20Space%20Odyssey%20with%20American%20film%20director%20Stanley%20Kubrick%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.celestis.com%2Flaunch-schedule%2Ftranquility-flight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Celestis's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelestis's%20moon%20service%20starts%20at%20about%20%2413%2C000%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.celestis.com%2Fexperiences-pricing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20its%20website.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20human%20remains%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20space%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20the%20first%20time%20Gene%20Roddenberry's%20cremated%20remains%20have%20flown%20above%20our%20planet.%20The%20screenwriter%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20first%20human%20%26quot%3Bspace%20burial%26quot%3B%20in%201992%20when%20his%20ashes%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2F78x73q%2Fthe-ashes-of-dead-people-orbiting-earth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20aboard%20NASA's%20spacecraft%20Columbia.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20launch%20has%20been%20controversial%2C%20drawing%20ire%20in%20particular%20from%20the%20Navajo%20Nation%2C%20who%20see%20the%20moon%20as%20sacred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20NASA%20said%20that%20the%20mission%20is%20privately%20owned%20and%20that%20the%20agency%20has%20no%20say%20in%20the%20other%20payload%20on%20board%2C%20per%20Space.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThornton%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20Astrobotic%2C%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20he%20was%20disappointed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20conversation%20came%20up%20so%20late%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F01%2F08%2Fscience%2Fvulcan-rocket-launch-moon.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr.%20Thornton%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20we%20can%20find%20a%20good%20path%20forward%20with%20the%20Navajo%20Nation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Peregrine%20isn't%20just%20carrying%20human%20remains.%20NASA's%20payload%20on%20board%20also%20includes%20instruments%20that%20will%20set%20out%20to%20measure%20water%20molecules%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20as%20well%20as%20radiation%2C%20and%20gases%20around%20the%20lander.%20They%20will%20investigate%20the%20exosphere%2C%20a%20thin%20layer%20of%20gases%20that%20floats%20around%20the%20moon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fmissions%2Fartemis%2Fclps%2Fnasa-sending-five-payloads-to-moon-on-astrobotics-peregrine-lander%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20a%20NASA%20press%20release.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D