s%20a%20loaded%20phrase%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-biden-china-going-take-over-taiwan-war-report-apec-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeijing%20warns%20such%20a%20move%20%26quot%3Bmeans%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20race%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWho's%20in%20the%20running%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20basically%20a%20three-way%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELai%20of%20the%20DPP%20is%20vying%20to%20succeed%20his%20boss%2C%20the%20outgoing%20Tsai%2C%20and%20has%20been%20vice%20president%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years.%20Beijing%20is%20extremely%20critical%20of%20Lai%2C%20who%20called%20himself%20a%20%26quot%3Bpragmatic%20worker%20for%20Taiwan%20independence%26quot%3B%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20joined%20by%20Bi-khim%20Hsiao%2C%20the%20vice-presidential%20candidate%20who's%20a%20famous%20figure%20in%20Washington%2C%20having%20served%20as%20Taiwan's%C2%A0de%20facto%C2%A0ambassador%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELai%2C%20a%2064-year-old%20Harvard%20graduate%2C%20hails%20from%20a%20humble%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20died%20in%20a%20mining%20accident%20when%20he%20was%20not%20yet%20a%20year%20old%2C%20and%20he%20was%20among%20six%20children%20raised%20by%20his%20mother.%20Before%20he%20became%20vice%20president%2C%20he%20was%20the%20mayor%20of%20Tainan%20and%20later%20Taiwan's%20premier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Beijing-friendly%20front%2C%20the%20KMT%2C%20or%20Nationalist%20Party%2C%20is%20represented%20by%20Hou%2C%20a%20former%20police%20officer%20who%20is%20the%20mayor%20of%20New%20Taipei%20City%2C%20just%20outside%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHou%2C%20however%2C%20is%20viewed%20with%20skepticism%20by%20some%20in%20the%20KMT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hou%20Yu-ih%2C%20Taiwan%20presidential%20candidate%20from%20the%20main%20opposition%20Kuomintang%20(KMT)%2C%20is%20greeted%20by%20supporters%20during%20a%20campaign%20rally%20in%20Kaohsiung%20on%20January%207%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659bdb0c6979d73718212a35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223326%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHou%20Yu-ih%2C%20the%20Taiwanese%20presidential%20candidate%20from%20the%20main%20opposition%20Kuomintang%20party%2C%20being%20greeted%20by%20supporters%20during%20a%20campaign%20rally%20on%20Sunday.%3Cp%3ESAM%20YEH%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20KMT%2C%20the%20hardcore%20supporters%20believe%20in%20a%20pan-Chinese%20identity%2C%20as%20many%20of%20their%20families%20came%20from%20the%20mainland%20and%20moved%20to%20Taiwan%20reluctantly%20only%20after%20the%20Communist%20takeover%20in%201949.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHou's%20family%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20had%20been%20in%20Taiwan%20for%20generations%2C%20and%20is%20considered%20as%20native%20Taiwanese%20instead%20of%20Chinese%20from%20mainland%20provinces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tension%20prompted%20Hou%20to%20show%20proof%20of%20his%20father's%20record%20as%20a%20KMT%20veteran%20and%20warship%20repairer%20during%20fighting%20against%20the%20Communists%20in%20the%201940s%2C%20even%20though%20he%20was%20also%20conscripted%20by%20the%20Imperial%20Japanese%20Army%20during%20the%20colonization%20of%20Taiwan.%20After%20the%20wars%2C%20his%20father%20became%20a%20butcher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20third%20party%20this%20time%20(which%20is%20not%20always%20the%20case)%3A%20the%20Taiwan%20People's%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20former%20Mayor%20Ko%20Wen-je%20of%20Taipei%2C%20who's%20especially%20popular%20among%20young%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20claims%20to%20occupy%20the%20middle%20ground%20between%20the%20two%20traditional%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20do%20the%20polls%20say%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20clear%20favorite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan%20has%20a%2010-day%20blackout%20period%20on%20polls%20ahe