%20in%20Taiwan%20over%20Beijing's%20heavy-handed%20response%20to%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20protests%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20president%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20parliament%2C%20or%20the%20Legislative%20Yuan%2C%20is%20also%20up%20for%20grabs%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20with%20the%20113%20lawmakers%20to%20be%20chosen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TPP%20vows%20to%20win%20enough%20seats%20to%20block%20either%20the%20DPP%20or%20the%20KMT%20from%20securing%20a%20simple%20majority%2C%20though%20polling%20remains%20inconclusive%20whether%20this%20would%20be%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELai%2C%20the%20sitting%20vice%20president%20running%20as%20a%20candidate%2C%20appealed%20on%20Saturday%20to%20supporters%20to%20back%20all%20DPP%20candidates%20in%20the%20legislative%20poll%20too%2C%20warning%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20run%20the%20country%20efficiently%20if%20his%20party%20failed%20to%20take%20at%20least%20half%20of%20the%20legislature's%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhen%20will%20we%20know%20the%20result%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20announced%20at%2010%3A30%20p.m.%20(9%3A30%20a.m.%20ET)%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20polls%20close%20at%204%20p.m.%2C%20counting%20begins%20and%20is%20constantly%20updated%2C%20so%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20clarity%20before%20the%20final%20official%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20at%20stake%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20election%C2%A0forms%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20geopolitical%20rivalry%20between%20China%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Beijing%20has%20been%20beefing%20up%20its%20military%20for%20any%20conflict%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20Chinese%20officials%20have%20also%20stressed%20military%20options%20are%20a%20last%20resort%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20in%20public%20statements%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20if%20peaceful%20reunification%20is%20no%20longer%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20ruling%20DPP%20wins%2