%20at%20an%20antique%20market%20for%20%2425.%20It's%20now%20expected%20to%20sell%20for%20up%20to%20%2419%2C000.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20antique%20brooch%20designed%20by%20William%20Burges%20in%20a%20photo%20published%20by%20Gildings%20Auctioneers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659bd1b5ec62ab5daf816a23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20antique%20brooch%20designed%20by%20William%20Burges%20in%20a%20photo%20published%20by%20Gildings%20Auctioneers.%3Cp%3EGildings%20Auctioneers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFlora%20Steel%20bought%20a%20brooch%20at%20an%20antique%20market%20decades%20ago%20for%20around%20%2425.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20old%20clip%20of%C2%A0%26quot%3BAntiques%20Roadshow%26quot%3B%20she%20watched%20revealed%20that%20it%20was%20made%20by%20a%20famous%20designer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20now%20projected%20to%20sell%20for%20up%20to%20%2419%2C000%20at%20auction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2035%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20woman%20purchased%20a%20brooch%20at%20an%20English%20antique%20market%20for%20less%20than%20%C2%A320%2C%20or%20around%20%2425.%20It's%20now%20projected%20to%20sell%20for%20up%20to%20%2419%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20an%20astonishing%2075%2C900%25%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlora%20Steel%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20the%20brooch%20when%20she%20bought%20it%20in%201988%2C%20but%20after%20watching%20an%20old%20clip%20of%20the%20BBC's%20%26quot%3BAntiques%20Roadshow%26quot%3B%20recently%20she%20realized%20that%20it%20might%20have%20been%20designed%20by%20the%2019th-century%20Gothic%20Revival%20designer%20William%20Burges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BAntiques%20Roadshow%26quot%3B%20clip%20from%202011%20that%20Steel%20watched%20showed%20Geoffrey%20Munn%2C%20a%20jewelry%20expert%2C%20exhibiting%20a%20series%20of%20brooch%20designs%20by%20Burges%2C%20who%20Munn%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20greatest%20genius%20of%2019th-century%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gildings.co.uk%2Fnews-item%2Four-remarkable-story-with-burges-brooches-continues%2F%3Fpc%3D63%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20Gildings%20Auctioneers.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurges%20is%20perhaps%20best%20known%20for%20remodeling%20Cardiff%20Castle%20in%20Wales%2C%20though%20he%20also%20designed%20metalwork%2C%20jewelry%2C%20and%20sculptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20clip%2C%20a%20woman%20displayed%20one%20of%20Burges's%20designs%2C%20her%20own%20silver%2C%20turquoise%2C%20and%20garnet%20brooch%2C%20before%20having%20it%20valued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Gildings%20Auctioneers%2C%20it%20was%20valued%20at%20%2410%2C000%20and%20sold%20at%20auction%20in%202011%20for%20%C2%A331%2C000%2C%20or%20nearly%20%2440%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Steel%20watched%20the%20compilation%20of%20the%20show's%20best%20finds%2C%20she%20noticed%20her%20brooch%20closely%20resembled%20the%20one%20featured%20in%20the%20clip%2C%20according%20to%20the%20auction%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20brooch%20originally%20caught%20my%20eye%20for%20its%20strong%20design%2C%20strange%20lettering%2C%20and%20unusual%20stones%2C%26quot%3B%20Steel%20said%2C%20according%20to%20Gildings%20Auctioneers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20loved%20it%20and%20thought%20that%20it%20was%20so%20particular%20in%20its%20design%20that%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20I%20would%20discover%20who%20had%20designed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteel%20reached%20out%20to%20Gildings%20Auctioneers%2C%20which%20confirmed%20that%20Burges%20designed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20clear%20this%20was%20another%20one%20of%20the%20designs%20on%20the%20page%20of%20sketches%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Will%20Gilding%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20auction%20house%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteel's%20brooch%20was%20f