20emerged%20for%20travellers%20at%20Indian%20airports%3A%20the%20%E2%80%98mandatory%E2%80%99%20implementation%20of%20DigiYatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDigiYatra%2C%20a%20biometric%20face%20scanning%20system%2C%20has%20sparked%20concerns%20and%20confusion%20among%20travellers.%20Many%20were%20uninformed%20about%20why%20their%20faces%20were%20being%20scanned%20or%20why%20participation%20was%20compulsory.%20This%20system%2C%20already%20operational%20in%2013%20airports%2C%20is%20set%20to%20expand%20nationwide%2C%20prompting%20urgent%20questions%20about%20its%20implications%20for%20privacy%2C%20data%20security%2C%20and%20civil%20liberties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20seasoned%20lawyer%20with%20deep%20insights%20into%20the%20intersection%20of%20technology%2C%20law%2C%20and%20civil%20rights%2C%20spearheads%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20called%20%E2%80%9C1984.%E2%80%9D%20The%20channel%2C%20named%20after%20George%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20dystopian%20novel%2C%20delves%20into%20the%20impact%20of%20digital%20technologies%20on%20democracy%20in%20India.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4DkLMc8faEk%26t%3D278s%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3Erecent%20video%2C%20Gupta%20dissected%20the%20complexities%20of%20DigiYatra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raising%20critical%20issues%20about%20its%20governance%2C%20data%20privacy%2C%20and%20potential%20for%20abuse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F4DkLMc8faEk%3Fsi%3DWSE5n0kHd7g_p73_%26start%3D299%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDigiYatra%20traces%20its%20origins%20back%20to%202018%2C%20with%20its%20primary%20objective%20being%20a%20seamless%2C%20contactless%20airport%20experience%20through%20facial%20recognition.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20claims%20that%20privacy%20concerns%20have%20been%20addressed%2C%20citing%20a%20decentralised%2C%20mobile%20wallet-based%20identity%20management%20system.%20However%2C%20Gupta%20expressed%20skepticism%2C%20pointing%20to%20significant%20gaps%20in%20these%20assurances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DigiYatra%20Foundation%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20established%20in%202019%2C%20administers%20the%20system.%20Its%20unique%20composition%20%E2%80%93%20a%20blend%20of%20public%20and%20private%20entities%20%E2%80%93%20complicates%20accountability.%20While%20the%20government%20holds%20a%2026%25%20stake%20through%20the%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%2C%20the%20rest%20is%20divided%20among%20major%20airports.%20This%20arrangement%2C%20Gupta%20argued%2C%20creates%20a%20quasi-monopolistic%20entity%20that%20lacks%20the%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20typically%20expected%20of%20public%20institutions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20implementation%20model%20of%20DigiYatra%20raises%20questions%20about%20preferential%20treatment%20and%20the%20monetisation%20of%20passenger%20data.%20Gupta%20underscored%20the%20potential%20for%20airports%20to%20prioritise%20Digi%20Yatra%20users%2C%20thereby%20subtly%20coercing%20more%20travellers%20to%20opt%20into%20the%20system.%20The%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20model%2C%20which%20includes%20using%20passenger%20data%20for%20marketing%20hotels%2C%20taxis%2C%20and%20other%20services%2C%20further%20blurs%20the%20line%20between%20security%20and%20commercial%20exploitation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdigi-yatra-privacy-biometric-travel%5C%22%3EHow%20%E2%80%98Digi%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20Can%20Potentially%20Be%20Used%20To%20Police%20Your%20Travel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20privacy%20front%2C%20Gupta%20highlighted%20the%20absence%20of%20regulatory%20oversight%2C%20despite%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023.%20The%20act%E2%80%99s%20loopholes%20and%20the%20non-application%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20to%20the%20DigiYatra%20Foundation%20obscure%20the%20system%E2%80%99s%20data%20handling%20practices.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20public%20audits%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20data%20misuse%20raise%20alarms%20about%20the%20security%20of%20sensitive%20biometric%20information.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%E2%80%99s%20critique%20extended%20beyond%20privacy%20concerns%2C%20touching%20on%20broader%20implications%20for%20democratic%20freedoms.%20He%20warns%20of%20a%20future%20where%20DigiYatra%20becomes%20a%20ubiquitous%20ID%2C%20required%20for%20everyday%20activities%20enabling%20pervasive%20state%20surveillance.%20This%20scenario%2C%20while%20speculative%2C%20is%20not%20unfounded%2C%20given%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20ambitions%20to%20expand%20DigiYatra%E2%80%99s%20applications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20Gupta%20called%20for%20public%20awareness%20and%20scrutiny.%20By%20sharing%20experiences%20and%20voicing%20concerns%2C%20citizens%20can%20challenge%20the%20encroaching%20reach%20of%20Digiyatra%20and%20demand%20transparency%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704715254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F13172957%2FUntitled-design-25.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fdigiyatra-the-promise-and-perils-of-indias-new-airport-biometric-system%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20biometric%20face%20scanning%20system%20has%20sparked%20concerns%20and%20confusion%20among%20travellers.%20Many%20were%20uninformed%20about%20why%20their%20faces%20were%20being%20scanned%20or%20why%20participation%20w