0the%20matter%20their%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20opinion%20that%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20views%20of%20the%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20the%20archipelago%20nation%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20strained%20after%20Mr%20Muizzu%20came%20to%20power.%20Seen%20as%20a%20pro-China%20politician%2C%20Mr%20Muizzu%20had%20defeated%20his%20India-friendly%20predecessor%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20in%20the%20presidential%20run-off%20held%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltimes.cn%2Fpage%2F202401%2F1304934.shtml%5C%22%3Eeditorial%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Global%20Times%20says%20China%20has%20always%20treated%20the%20Maldives%20as%20an%20equal%20partner%20and%20respected%20its%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20respects%20the%20friendly%20and%20cooperative%20relationship%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20India%2C%20fully%20aware%20of%20the%20importance%20for%20Male%20to%20maintain%20good%20relations%20with%20New%20Delhi.%20Beijing%20has%20never%20asked%20Male%20to%20reject%20New%20Delhi%20because%20of%20the%20conflicts%20between%20China%20and%20India%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20view%20cooperation%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20India%20as%20unfriendly%20or%20a%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chinese%20state%20media%20editorial%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(China)%20is%20also%20willing%20to%20carry%20out%20trilateral%20cooperation%20between%20China%2C%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives.%20New%20Delhi%20should%20stay%20more%20open-minded%2C%20as%20China's%20cooperation%20with%20South%20Asian%20countries%20is%20not%20a%20zero-sum%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Muizzu's%20predecessors%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20visited%20India%20first%2C%20considering%20the%20wide-ranging%20bilateral%20ties%20and%20the%20Maldives'%20proximity%20to%20India%2C%20followed%20by%20China%20which%20has%20expanded%20its%20influence%20in%20the%20island%20nation%20by%20investing%20in%20major%20infrastructure%20projects%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20normal%20circumstances%2C%20when%20a%20new%20leader%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20they%20arrange%20their%20visits%20based%20on%20the%20importance%20and%20urgency%20of%20the%20matters%20to%20be%20dealt%20with.%20President%20Muizzu%20broke%20tradition%20by%20visiting%20Turkey%20for%20his%20first%20official%20overseas%20visit%20instead%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Global%20Times%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Muizzu%2C%20accompanied%20by%20wife%20Sajidha%20Mohamed%2C%20visited%20the%20Xiamen%20Free%20Trade%20Zone%20in%20China's%20Fujian%20province%20today%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%20Representatives%20from%20the%20Xiamen%20Free%20Trade%20Zone%20presented%20an%20introductory%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Muizzu%20is%20due%20to%20hold%20talks%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20and%20sign%20several%20agreements%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Wang%20Wenbin.%20%26quot%3BThe%20relations%20between%20China%20and%20the%20Maldives%20now%20stand%20at%20a%20new%20historical%20starting%20point.%20We%20believe%20that%20through%20this%20visit%2C%20the%20two%20heads%20of%20state%20will%20provide%20strategic%20guidance%20for%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20to%20reach%20a%20new%20height%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20told%20the%20media%20on%20January%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704707400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fivvmortg_mohamed-muizzu_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-zero-sum-game-china-on-ties-with-maldives-amid-india-row-4822417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20a%20day%20Maldives'%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20landed%20in%20Beijing%20to%20sign%20bilateral%20agreements%2C%20China's%20state%20media%20in%20an%20editorial%20referred%20to%20India's%20diplomatic%20row%20with%20the%20Maldives%2C%20a