Animal'%20celebrated%20its%20phenomenal%20success.%20A%20touching%20moment%20captured%20in%20a%20viral%20video%20showed%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20touching%20the%20feet%20of%20actor%20and%20acting%20coach%20Saurabh%20Sachdeva%2C%20who%20portrayed%20Abid%20Haque%20in%20the%20film.%20Sachdeva's%20performance%20has%20earned%20widespread%20acclaim%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20film's%20monumental%20success%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20Sachdeva%2C%20known%20for%20his%20remarkable%20stint%20as%20an%20acting%20coach%2C%20has%20trained%20numerous%20renowned%20artists%2C%20including%20Rana%20Daggubati%20and%20Varun%20Dhawan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwatch-ranbir-kapoors-respectful-gesture-steals-the-show-at-animal-success-bash%2Farticleshow%2F106634659.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Unites%20the%20Air%20of%20Asia's%20Cities%3F%20An%20Invisible%20Killer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08131855%2FScreenshot-2024-01-08-at-1.18.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20deaths%20increase%20by%20150%2C000%20in%20rapidly%20growing%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20people%20in%20cities%20in%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20face%20the%20threat%20of%20dying%20prematurely%20due%20to%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighteen%20cities%20in%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20tropical%20region%20are%20growing%20fast%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20home%20to%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1177%2F0956247816663557%5C%22%3E10%20million%20people%20each%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%202100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20have%20limited%20to%20no%20routine%20ground%20monitoring%20of%20air%20pollution%20making%20it%20challenging%20to%20work%20out%20how%20bad%20the%20air%20has%20become%20resulting%20from%20this%20rapid%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20increase%20due%20to%20insufficient%20control%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20inadequate%20funding%20for%20monitoring%20pollutants%20such%20as%20nitrogen%20dioxide%20and%20ammonia%20that%20also%20form%20harmful%20fine%20particles%20(PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20hazardous%20pollutant%20of%20them%20all%20is%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%2C%20which%20penetrates%20deep%20into%20the%20lungs%20and%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20impact%20just%20about%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournal.chestnet.org%2Farticle%2FS0012-3692(18)32723-5%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3Eevery%20organ%20in%20the%20human%20body%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Long-term%20exposure%20to%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.abm4435%5C%22%3Ewas%20linked%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20149%2C000%20early%20deaths%20in%20South%20Asian%20cities%20and%2053%2C000%20in%20Southeast%20Asian%20cities%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20increased%20by%20126%2C000%20to%20275%2C000%20in%20South%20Asian%20cities%20and%20by%2026%2C000%20to%2080%2C000%20in%20Southeast%20Asian%20cities%20in%202018.%20Dhaka%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20Mumbai%20and%20Bangalore%20in%20India%20had%20the%20largest%20increase%20in%20early%20deaths%20from%20long-term%20exposure%20to%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20increase%20in%20early%20deaths%20in%20South%20Asian%20cities%20is%20the%20combined%20result%20of%20both%20increasing%20populations%20and%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0levels%20from%202005%20to%202018.%20For%20cities%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20population%20increase%20played%20a%20much%20larger%20role%20in%20the%20increase%20than%20change%20in%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20findings%20of%20the%20study%2C%20which%20focused%20only%20on%20the%20tropical%20region%2C%20suggest%20that%20even%20if%20the%20air%20pollution%20levels%20remain%20the%20same%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20urban%20population%20in%20these%20fast-growing%20cities%20will%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20exposure%20to%20harmful%20pollutants%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20early%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20anticipated%20rapid%20urban%20expansion%20throughout%20this%20century%2C%20the%20issue%20could%20be%20exacerbated%20unless%20new%20measures%20are%20implemented%20to%20mitigate%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20increased%20interest%20in%20low-cost%20sensors%2C%20these%20are%20prone%20to%20biases%20and%20are%20relatively%20recent%20and%20so%20do%20not%20provide%20information%20about%20the%20changes%20in%20air%20pollution%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstruments%20on%20board%20satellites%20are%20the%20eyes%20in%20the%20skies%20which%20provide%20a%20long%20record%20and%20an%20extensive%20coverage%20of%20air%20pollution.%20Data%20from%20space-based%20instruments%20is%20publicly%20available%20for%20a%20suite%20of%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20effective%20these%20satellite%20observations%20are%20for%20monitoring%20air%20pollution%20in%20cities%20has%20been%20well%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facp.copernicus.org%2Farticles%2F21%2F6275%2F2021%2F%5C%22%3Eevaluated%20against%20ground-based%20monitors%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0where%20these%20are%20available%2C%20prompting%20greater%20use%20of%20satellites%20where%20ground-based%20monitoring%20is%20lacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.abm4435%5C%22%3ESatellite%20observations%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0collected%20between%202005%20and%202018%20by%20NASA%20and%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20show%20increasing%20levels%20of%20most%20air%20pollutants%20across%20the%2018%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20study%2C%20the%20cities%20analysed%20were%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bangalore%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Chittagong%2C%20Dhaka%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Karachi%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%20and%20Surat%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20Bangkok%2C%20Hanoi%2C%20Ho%20Chi%20Minh%20City%2C%20Jakarta%2C%20Manila%2C%20Phnom%20Penh%20and%20Yangon%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20cities%20in%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20show%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20nitrogen%20dioxide%20that%20directly%20impacts%20health%2C%20along%20with%20forming%20health-hazardous%20ozone%20and%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitrogen%20dioxide%20levels%20tripled%20in%20Chittagong%20(Bangladesh)%20and%20doubled%20in%20Dhaka%20(Bangladesh)%20and%20Hanoi%20(Vietnam)%20over%20the%2014-year%20period.%20These%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20increase%20in%20emissions%20from%20vehicular%20traffic%20and%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJakarta%20in%20Indonesia%20is%20the%20only%20city%20with%20a%20decline%20in%20nitrogen%20dioxide%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20success%20of%20air%20quality%20measures%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.academia.edu%2F1362194%2FEvaluating_the_Effects_of_a_New_Vehicle_Emission_Standard_on_Urban_Air_Quality_in_Jakarta_City%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20in%202005%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgricultural%20emissions%20linked%20to%20livestock%20and%20fertilisers%20are%20typically%20unregulated%20and%20are%20the%20dominant%20sources%20of%20ammonia%2C%20a%20respiratory%20irritant%20which%20is%20also%20a%20precursor%20of%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20ammonia%20from%20urban%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreases%20in%20nitrogen%20dioxide%20and%20ammonia%20levels%20drive%20the%20increases%20in%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E.%20There%20is%20a%20large%20and%20significant%20increase%20of%20up%20to%208%20percent%20each%20year%20in%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0levels%20in%20Indian%20cities%20with%20PM%3Csub%3E2.5%3C%2Fsub%3E%C2%A0increasing%20to%20more%20than%20double%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20Hyderabad%20from%202005%20to%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20observations%20are%20at%20a%20very%20coarse%20resolution%20of%20about%20tens%20of%20kilometres%20and%20with%20limited%20ground%20monitoring%2C%20air%20pollution%20sources%20can%20only%20be%20speculated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20centuries%2C%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20have%20grappled%20with%20air%20pollution%20primarily%20stemming%20from%20the%20widespread%20practice%20of%20open%20burning%20of%20agricultural%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20commonly%20burn%20vegetation%20during%20the%20dry%20season%20to%20clear%20land%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20upcoming%20sowing%20season.%20The%20smoke%20from%20these%20fires%20is%20laden%20with%20pollutants%2C%20posing%20risks%20to%20both%20human%20health%20and%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20looking%20at%20cities%2C%20where%20most%20people%20live%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shift%20from%20rural%20to%20urban%20sources%20of%20pollution%20such%20as%20road%20traffic%20and%20burning%20of%20waste%20and%20household%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20mitigation%20measures%20are%20one%20of%20the%20challenges%20facing%20Asian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20measures%20encompass%20enhanced%20ground%20monitoring%20capabilities%20to%20pinpoint%20local%20sources%20of%20air%20pollution%2C%20as%20well%20as%20regulating%20uncontrolled%20emissions%20such%20as%20those%20from%20agriculture%2C%20which%20contribute%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20more%20harmful%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accessibility%20of%20emission%20control%20technologies%20has%20become%20more%20affordable%20and%20easier%20than%20ever.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20learn%20from%20past%20mistakes%20and%20take%20action%20now%20to%20prevent%20an%20imminent%20health%20crisis%20in%20these%20rapidly%20growing%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDr%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ucl.ac.uk%2Fgeography%2Fkarn-vohra%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EKarn%20Vohra%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Research%20Fellow%20at%20University%20College%20London.%20He%20has%20a%20PhD%20in%20Environmental%20Health%20and%20Risk%20Management%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Birmingham.%20His%20research%20focuses%20on%20the%20application%20of%20ground-based%20and%20satellite%20observations%2C%20chemical%20transport%20models%20and%20health%20risk%20assessment%20models%20to%20improve%20the%20understanding%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20its%20sources%20on%20public%20health.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHe%20received%20funding%20for%20his%20research%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Birmingham%20Global%20Challenges%20Studentship.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOriginally%20published%20under%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0by%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E360info%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%84%A2.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704706255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08131855%2FScreenshot-2024-01-08-at-1.18.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fwhat-unites-the-air-of-asias-cities-an-invisible-killer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accessibility%20of%20emission%20control%20technologies%20has%20become%20more%20affordable%20and%20easier%20than%20ever.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20learn%20from%20past%20mistakes%20and%20take%20action%20now%20to%20prevent%20an%20imminent%20health%20crisis%20in%20these%20rapidly%20growing%20cities.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fwhat-unites-the-air-of-asias-cities-an-invisible-killer%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20Reacted%20To%20Unsealing%20Of%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20Case%20Files%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EGhislaine%20Maxwell%2C%20a%20convicted%20sex%20trafficker%20and%20the%20partner%20of%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%2C%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20release%20of%20court%20documents%20revealing%20the%20names%20of%20associates%20of%20the%20paedophile.%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20is%20currently%20serving%20a%2020-year%20sentence%20for%20her%20role%20in%20helping%C2%A0Jeffrey%20Epstein%20in%20recruiting%20and%20groom%20underage%20girls%20as%20part%20of%20their%20sex%20trafficking%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20her%20attorneys%2C%20Arthur%20Aidala%20and%20Diana%20Fabi%20Samson%2C%20Ms%20Maxwell%20declared%20her%20intention%20to%20proceed%20with%20an%20appeal%20for%20the%20dismissal%20of%20case%20filed%20against%20her%20by%C2%A0Virginia%20Giuffre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20attorneys%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9CGhislaine%20Maxwell%20took%20no%20position%20on%20the%20Court's%20recent%20decision%20to%20unseal%20documents%20in%20Giuffre%20v.%20Maxwell%20as%20these%20disclosures%20have%20no%20bearing%20on%20her%20or%20her%20pending%20appeal.%20Ghislaine's%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20upcoming%20appellate%20argument%20asking%20for%20her%20entire%20case%20to%20be%20dismissed.%20She%20is%20confident%20that%20she%20will%20obtain%20justice%20in%20the%20Second%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals.%20She%20has%20consistently%20and%20vehemently%20maintained%20her%20innocence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Independent%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20significant%20ruling%20by%20US%20District%20Judge%20Loretta%20Preska%20allowed%20the%20release%20of%20documents%2C%20including%20the%20unsealing%20of%20names%2C%20after%20January%201.%20While%20the%20judge%20protected%20the%20identities%20of%20some%20Epstein%20victims%2C%20she%20insisted%20that%20the%20names%20of%20Epstein's%20associates%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BJohn%20and%20Jane%20Does%2C%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20decision%20has%20brought%20several%20well-known%20figures%20into%20the%20spotlight%2C%20including%20former%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20Stephen%20Hawking%2C%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%20and%20Donald%20Trump.%20In%20a%20recently%20unsealed%20deposition%2C%20Johanna%20Sjoberg%20testified%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5BEpstein%5D%20said%20one%20time%20that%20Clinton%20likes%20them%20young%2C%E2%80%9D%20referring%20to%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENew%20details%20have%20emerged%20from%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell's%20case%20following%20the%20unsealing%20of%20documents%2C%20revealing%20that%20she%20did%20not%20attend%20a%20deposition%20after%20being%20subpoenaed%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20disgraced%20British%20socialite%20was%20summoned%20to%20testify%20in%20a%20case%20initiated%20by%20Virginia%20Giuffre.%20Ms%20Maxwell%2C%20who%20initially%20agreed%20to%20participate%2C%20cited%20family%20affairs%20in%20the%20UK%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20unavailability%2C%20later%20informing%20Ms%20Giuffre's%20team%20that%20she%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20due%20to%20her%20mother's%20illness.%20However%2C%20a%20photo%20released%20in%202010%20showed%20Ms%20Maxwell%20attending%20the%20wedding%20of%20Chelsea%20Clinton%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20around%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704706200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7o9cl6l_jeffrey-epstein-afp_625x300_05_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-ghislaine-maxwell-reacted-to-unsealing-of-jeffrey-epstein-files-4822163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20is%20currently%20serving%20a%2020-year%