20event%2C%20in%20one%20of%20his%20last%20major%20efforts%20to%20draw%20investments%20before%20a%20re-election%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20Global%20Summit%20during%20Jan.%2010-12%20is%20expected%20to%20bring%20in%20around%20100%2C000%20visitors%2C%20including%20chief%20executives%2C%20business%20leaders%2C%20ministers%20and%20diplomats%20from%20133%20countries%2C%20in%20what%20organizers%20have%20dubbed%20as%20the%20biggest%20ever%20gathering%20at%20the%20biennial%20event%20which%20is%20in%20its%2010th%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20foreign%20companies%20taking%20part%20include%20Microsoft%2C%20Nasdaq%2C%20Alphabet's%20Google%2C%20Suzuki%20and%20Toyota.%20Gautam%20Adani%20and%20Mukesh%20Ambani%2C%20Asia's%20two%20richest%20people%2C%20and%20the%20chairman%20of%20salt-to-aviation%20conglomerate%20Tata%20Group%2C%20will%20be%20among%20the%20scores%20of%20top%20executives%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20investors%20have%20bet%20big%20on%20India%20since%20PM%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20-%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Apple%2C%20Samsung%2C%20Kia%20and%20Airbus%20expanding%20operations.%20This%2C%20even%20as%20some%20executives%20say%20his%20protectionist%20policies%20for%20sectors%20such%20as%20digital%20payments%2C%20manufacturing%20and%20e-commerce%20often%20promote%20local%20businesses%20to%20the%20disadvantage%20of%20foreign%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Gujarat%20officials%2C%20the%20summit%20will%20present%20a%20chance%20to%20attract%20investors%20to%20sectors%20such%20as%20chipmaking%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20manufacturing%20where%20India%20lags%2C%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20set%20to%20hold%20closed-door%20meetings%20with%20many%20executives%2C%20state%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20one%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20last%20big%20attempts%20to%20assure%20investors%20about%20his%20business%20friendly%20policies%20and%20bolster%20India's%20reputation%20as%20an%20investment%20destination%2C%20just%20months%20before%20the%202024%20national%20elections%2C%20where%20he%20will%20fight%20for%20a%20third%20term%20and%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20companies%20%26quot%3Bare%20factoring%20in%20that%20the%20current%20government%20will%20come%20back%20in%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mukesh%20Aghi%2C%20President%20of%20trade%20group%20US-India%20Strategic%20Partnership%20Forum%20which%20is%20leading%20its%20biggest%20ever%20delegation%20of%2050-plus%20US%20firms%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20quietly%20de-risking%20from%20China%2C%20and%20so%20India%2C%20with%20its%20fast%20growing%20economy%2C%20becomes%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Mr%20Aghi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHotel%20Rooms%20Get%20Pricey%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Gandhinagar%20at%20a%20sprawling%20convention%20centre%20managed%20by%20Leela%20Palace%2C%20the%20luxury%20hotels%20group%20owned%20by%20Brookfield.%20Roads%20leading%20to%20the%20convention%20centre%20are%20being%20cleaned%20and%20repaired%2C%20with%20hoardings%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20photos%20plastered%20across%20to%20promote%20Gujarat%20as%20an%20investment%20hotspot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20has%20attracted%20roughly%20%2434%20billion%20in%20foreign%20investments%20between%202019%20and%202023%2C%20the%20third%20highest%20among%20states%20after%20Maharashtra%20-%20home%20to%20financial%20capital%20Mumbai%20-%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20whose%20capital%20Bengaluru%20is%20country's%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20the%20earlier%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20summits%2C%20hotel%20rooms%20are%20in%20short%20supply%20now%20and%20getting%20pricier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeeppreet%20Bindra%2C%20general%20manager%20at%20a%20hotel%20run%20by%20Marriott%20International%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20which%20is%20about%2030%20km%20away%20from%20Gandhinagar%20and%20where%20many%20of%20the%20summit%20visitors%20will%20be%20staying%2C%20said%20his%20daily%20room%20tariffs%20had%20surged%20to%20%24420%20a%20night%2C%20from%20the%20typical%20%24150%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisitors%20though%20will%20have%20to%20largely%20skip%20alcohol%20as%20the%20state%20is%20one%20of%20few%20that%20restricts%20public%20liquor%20sales%2C%20unless%20special%20government%20permits%20are%20obtained%20-%20something%20that%20has%20often%20irked%20executives%20working%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20event%2C%20Gujarat%20signed%20initial%20investment%20pacts%20worth%20%24120%20billion%20with%20more%20than%20200%20companies%2C%20including%20steelmaker%20ArcelorMittal's%20local%20joint%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20mainly%20focused%20on%20traditional%20industries%20so%20far%2C%20but%20now%20we%20are%20also%20focusing%20on%20upcoming%20sectors%20such%20as%20semiconductors%2C%20electronics%20and%20EVs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul%20Gupta%20of%20state%20agency%20Gujarat%20Industrial%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704705120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0vdjkje8_vibrant-gujarat-global-summit-reuters_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-to-lure-tech-electric-vehicles-investments-at-gujarat-summit-as-poll-looms-4821710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20roll%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%20for%20hundreds%20of%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20investors%20visiting%20Gujarat%20this%20week%20for%20a%20business%20event%2C%20in%20one%20of%20his%20last%20major%20efforts%20to%20draw%20investments%20before%20a%20re-election%20bid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-to-lure-tech-