%20JD(U)%20Leader%20on%20No%20Decision%20on%20Convenor%20Appointment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145125%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-2.43.19-PM-e1693562152314.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20%E2%80%9Crunning%20out%20of%20time%20and%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20to%20outthink%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20said%20on%20Sunday%20(January%207).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20JD(U)%20chief%20national%20spokesperson%20K.C.%20Tyagi%20as%20saying%20that%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20would%20meet%20in%20%E2%80%9C10%20to%2015%20days%E2%80%9D%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20key%20posts%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdisappointing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20to%20show%20urgency%20to%20see%20a%20vibrant%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20has%20been%20pushing%20to%20get%20its%20party%20chief%20and%20Bihar%20chef%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20appointed%20the%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20convener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-renames-rahul-gandhis-bharat-nyay-yatra-as-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tyagi%20asked%20why%20the%20Congress%20was%20organising%20a%20yatra%20of%20its%20own%2C%20instead%20of%20turning%20it%20into%20an%20INDIA%20alliance%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20able%20to%20ensure%20a%20great%20build-up%20to%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%2C%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20offer%20a%20sound%20counter-narrative%20along%20demand%20of%20nationwide%20caste%20survey%20and%20other%20national%20issues.%20The%20Congress%20has%20embarked%20on%20its%20yatra.%20Rather%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20an%20INDIA%20Yatra%20in%20which%20all%20top%20alliance%20leaders%20could%20have%20participated.%20The%20Congress%20did%20not%20consult%20any%20of%20its%20allies%20before%20charting%20its%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20We%20welcome%20their%20yatra%20but%20it%20was%20not%20a%20good%20time%20to%20start%20it.%20INDIA%20is%20still%20in%20a%20confused%20state.%20What%20if%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20announced%20soon%20after%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20opening%3F%20We%20still%20do%20not%20have%20clarity%20on%20seat-sharing%2C%20agenda%2C%20and%20leadership%20roles.%20Congress%20should%20show%20its%20large-heartedness%2C%20shedding%20its%20big-brotherly%20attitude%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20reported%20the%20JD(U)%20leader%20as%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20way%20allies%20are%20going%20in%20different%20directions%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20serious%20concern%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-india-to-work-the-congress-must-take-a-step-back%5C%22%3EFor%20India%20to%20Work%2C%20the%20Congress%20Must%20Take%20a%20Step%20Back%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20West%20Bengal%20Congress%20chief%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhary%20demanded%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20after%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team%20was%20attacked%2C%20CPI%20MP%20Binoy%20Viswam%20questioned%20the%20propriety%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20contesting%20from%20Wayanad.%20The%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20been%20also%20sparring%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20Congress%20should%20take%20immediate%20steps%20to%20stop%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20from%20drifting%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20seat-sharing%20talks%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Telangana%20are%20the%20states%20where%20the%20Congress%20should%20try%20to%20accommodate%20its%20allies.%20We%20do%20want%20a%20stronger%20Congress%20but%20also%20a%20stronger%20INDIA%20bloc.%20The%20Congress%20should%20not%20also%20create%20confusion%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20by%20being%20reportedly%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20INDIA%20bloc%20leader%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20the%20convener%20would%20be%20responsible%20for%20taking%20crucial%20decisions%2C%20including%20seat-sharing%20among%20allies%20and%20devising%20campaign%20programmes%20in%20various%20states.%20He%20explained%20the%20distinction%20between%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20chairperson%20and%20the%20convenor.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20chairperson%20will%20only%20preside%20over%20meetings.%20Ahead%20of%20elections%2C%20the%20convener%E2%80%99s%20role%20will%20be%20very%20important%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20pitched%20for%20Kharge%20as%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate.%20This%20suggestion%20was%20backed%20by%20both%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kharge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ffriction-emerges-in-india-amid-push-for-kharge-as-pm-face-101703098628063.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20discussions%20on%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20and%20seat-sharing%20must%20precede%20any%20conversation%20on%20who%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20face%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20political%20life%2C%20I%20have%20never%20used%20my%20Dalit%20identity%20for%20any%20post.%20I%20am%20a%20worker%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Our%20first%20objective%20is%20to%20win%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EM