%20(RHPCL)%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20NHPC%20Limited%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20State%20Power%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20entered%20into%20a%20power%20purchase%20agreement%20with%20the%20Rajasthan%20Urja%20Vikas%20and%20IT%20Services%20Limited%20for%20offtake%20of%20electricity%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fstarved-of-power-jammu-and-kashmir-sells-power-40-year-rajasthan-deal-sparks-resource-rob-cry%2Fcid%2F1992085%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20This%20agreement%20was%20reportedly%20signed%20on%20January%203%20in%20Jaipur.%20It%20will%20be%20in%20place%20for%2040%20years%20from%20the%20date%20the%20project%20begins%20commercial%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20winter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F16-hour-long-power-cuts-kashmir-faces-unprecedented-crisis%5C%22%3Eit%20was%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20electricity%20production%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20hit%20a%20record%20low%20of%2050-100%20MegaWatts%20(MWs)%20against%20the%20demand%20of%201800%20MWs.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20valley%2C%20home%20to%20over%2070%20lakh%20people%2C%20is%20facing%2012-16%20hour%20long%20power%20cuts%20%E2%80%93%20the%20longest%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20reality%2C%20the%20contract%20to%20lease%20power%20to%20Rajasthan%20has%20created%20outrage%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20facing%20a%20severe%20power%20crisis%20never%20witnessed%20before%2C%20our%20hydro-electric%20resources%20are%20being%20outsourced%20to%20other%20states.%20Yet%20another%20decision%20that%20will%20rob%20people%20of%20basic%20amenities%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20collectively%20punish%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%E2%80%9D%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20People%E2%80%99s%20Democratic%20Party%20chief%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20too%20came%20out%20strongly%20against%20the%20plan%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9CNormally%2C%20power%20purchase%20agreements%20usually%20last%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%2020%20years.%20However%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20they%20are%20signing%20it%20for%2040%20years%20at%20a%20pre-negotiated%20price%2C%20which%20is%20also%20unknown.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20feeling%20of%20betrayal%20amongst%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20that%20their%20resources%20are%20being%20bartered%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20Apni%20Party%20president%20Altaf%20Bukhari%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20understand%20why%20such%20a%20decision%20had%20been%20taken.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20entire%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20facing%20an%20acute%20electricity%20crisis%2C%20especially%20in%20its%20rural%20areas%2C%20the%20reported%20leasing%20out%20of%20electricity%20from%20Rattle%20Power%20Project%20Kishtwar%20to%20Rajasthan%20is%20quite%20puzzling.%C2%A0The%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20has%20off%20and%20on%20came%20on%20record%20claiming%20that%20it%20has%20been%20buying%20the%20power%20supply%20from%20other%20states%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20leasing%20out%20its%20own%20supply%20to%20another%20state%20is%20beyond%20comprehension.%20I%20urge%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20to%20come%20clear%20on%20the%20facts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fjk-parties-up-in-arms-over-ratle-power-corporation-signing-deal-with-rajasthan-for-40-years%2Farticle67713192.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704691110000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08104747%2F83822154220221022822.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-a-winter-of-extr