%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20jute%20products%20have%20demand%20in%20India%20as%20well%20as%20abroad.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chaitali%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20noticed%20a%20police%20van%20with%20people%20disembarking%2C%20hands%20restrained%20with%20handcuffs%20and%20a%20thick%20rope%20around%20their%20waists%20%E2%80%93%20the%20customary%20way%20the%20accused%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20courtroom%20in%20those%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20my%20curiosity%20peaked%2C%20I%20approached%20one%20of%20my%20dad%E2%80%99s%20colleagues%20and%20asked%20who%20he%20was.%20Labelled%20as%20wrongdoers%2C%20they%20were%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20courtroom%20to%20face%20the%20consequences.%20I%20stood%20there%2C%20observing%20them%2C%20while%20their%20family%20members%20rushed%20towards%20them%2C%20engaging%20in%20fervent%20conversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20family%20members%E2%80%99%20suffering%2C%20little%20Chaitali%20felt%20like%20she%20should%20do%20something%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20too%20young%20but%20I%20had%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20that%20I%20want%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20age%2C%20Chaitali%20decided%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20social%20worker%20and%20chose%20the%20path%20of%20helping%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20Jute%20To%20the%20Global%20Stage%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20after%20several%20years%20of%20working%20with%20various%20NGOs%2C%20Chaitali%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Rakshak%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20focuses%20on%20empowering%20male%20and%20female%20inmates%20and%20other%20underprivileged%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20began%20my%20work%20at%20the%20correctional%20home%2C%20initially%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247834%2Ftechnology-teacher-training-madhya-pradesh-government-schools-english-classes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoken%20English%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20undertaken%20various%20projects%2C%20including%20activities%20such%20as%20cookie-making%20with%20women%20and%20inmates%2C%20introducing%20yoga%20(especially%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic)%2C%20engaging%20in%20woodwork%2C%20and%20conducting%20painting%20sessions.%20The%20array%20of%20projects%20reflects%20the%20diverse%20initiatives%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20involved%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20project%20that%20has%20gained%20significant%20traction%20is%20%E2%80%9CJute%20Story%20Beyond%20Bars%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22She%20has%20also%20trained%203000%20inmates%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20government.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337531%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20has%20also%20trained%203000%20inmates%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20government.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chaitali%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20especially%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20jute%20industry%20involves%20approximately%2040%20lakh%20people.%20We%20have%20actively%20engaged%20inmates%20in%20crafting%20jute%20products%2C%20showcasing%20their%20creations%20at%20various%20locations%2C%20including%20different%20chambers%20and%20events%20on%20both%20national%20and%20international%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20train%20and%20incubate%20these%20inmates%2C%20she%20connected%20with%20the%20National%20Jute%20Board%20of%20India%20(NJB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20program%20spans%2045%20days%2C%20and%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20partnered%20with%20NJB%20for%20its%20successful%20implementation.%20Our%20initial%20accomplishment%20was%20the%20training%20conducted%20at%20the%20Dandam%20Central%20Correctional%20Home%2C%20benefiting%20the%20prisoners%20there.%20Subsequently%2C%20I%20extended%20the%20initiative%20by%20providing%20additional%20training%2C%20leading%20to%20continued%20production%20and%20participation%20in%20various%20exhibitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20promote%20acceptance%20and%20usage%2C%20the%20organisation%20implemented%20a%20practice%20of%20free%20gifting%20initially.%20This%20strategy%20aims%20to%20introduce%20people%20to%20the%20products%2C%20fostering%20acceptance%20and%20encouraging%20reuse%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20this%20project%2C%20we%20have%20trained%20about%203%2C000%20inmates%20in%20making%20jute%20products.%20This%20project%20has%20evolved%20into%20%E2%80%98Root%20to%20Jute%E2%80%99.%20Notably%2C%20it%20has%20been%20incubated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrained%20and%20experienced%2C%20some%20of%20the%20inmates%20who%20have%20served%20their%20terms%20are%20even%20employed%20at%20Chaitali%E2%80%99s%20startup%2C%20becoming%20part%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F52355%2Fempowering-farmers-greenagtech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20management%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20produces%20jute%20products%20such%20as%20handicrafts%2C%20rugs%2C%20and%20handbags.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20and%20her%20foundation%20created%20the%20Guinness%20World%20Record%20for%20creating%20the%20largest%20jute%20bag%20in%20the%20world%20on%20January%207%2C%202021.%20The%20bag%20measures%2030.68%20m%20(100%20ft%208%20in)%20wide%20and%2024.87%20m%20(81%20ft%207%20in)%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20golden%20fibre%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20very%20popular%20among%20the%20youth%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20produces%20jute%20products%20such%20as%20handicrafts%2C%20rugs%2C%20and%20handbags.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337527%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20produces%20jute%20products%20such%20as%20handicrafts%2C%20rugs%2C%20and%20handbags.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chaitali%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20products%20specifically%20designed%20for%20young%20individuals.%20One%20effective%20way%20we%20showcase%20these%20products%20is%20through%20fashion-oriented%20presentations.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20feature%20scenarios%20where%20students%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20university%20or%20college%2C%20are%20seen%20carrying%20jute%20bags.%20This%20not%20only%20generates%20interest%20but%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20visual%20platform%20to%20display%20the%20products%20tailored%20for%20this%20age%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20her%20productions%20are%20going%20up%2C%20she%20still%20hopes%20that%20more%20people%20use%20jute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%20and%20pondering%20on%20why%20she%20chose%20inmates%20for%20this%20particular%20program%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20view%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20correctional%20system%20as%20wrongdoers%20or%20offenders%2C%20carrying%20a%20mindset%20that%20they%20deserve%20punishment.%20However%2C%20when%20these%20individuals%20engage%20in%20crafting%20products%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20environment%2C%20a%20shift%20in%20perception%20occurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20begin%20to%20appreciate%20the%20positive%20contributions%2C%20and%20gradually%2C%20acceptance%20grows.%20It%20becomes%20evident%20that%2C%20given%20a%20positive%20direction%2C%20individuals%20labelled%20as%20wrongdoers%20or%20convicts%20are%20capable%20of%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFind%20her%20work%20inspiring%3F%20Buy%20her%20products%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rakshakfoundation.in%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704378304000%2C%2