%2FHarvest-of-black-potatoes-1704205496-768x440.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FHarvest-of-black-potatoes-1704205496-150x86.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337291%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22468%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20harvesting%20the%20black%20potatoes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20black%20potato%20taste%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20a%20denser%20texture%20and%20are%20slightly%20nuttier%20than%20the%20usual%20white%20potatoes%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Maurya.%20Anand%20Mani%20Bhat%20(44)%20of%20Bhimtal%20village%20in%20Nainital%2C%20who%20took%20to%20growing%20black%20potatoes%20in%202021%2C%20agrees%20with%20Maurya%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20an%20interestingly%20earthier%20flavour%20than%20the%20usual.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Atul%20Singh%20of%20Jhansi%20was%20given%20a%20handful%20of%20black%20potatoes%20by%20Maurya%20about%20two%20years%20ago%20to%20try%20them%20out%2C%20he%20has%20been%20seeking%20them%20whenever%20they%20arrive%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2035-year-old%20trader%20of%20agricultural%20products%20online%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20fairly%20small%20compared%20to%20the%20regular%20potatoes%20which%20we%20have%20been%20using.%20When%20sliced%20open%2C%20it%20reveals%20a%20purple%20ring%20near%20the%20edge.%20I%20find%20it%20suitable%20for%20roasting%2C%20baking%20or%20steaming%20and%20have%20commonly%20made%20chips%20from%20it%20which%20is%20perfect%20for%20its%20sweet%20and%20buttery%20flavour%20and%20light%2C%20floury%20texture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSliced-pieces-of-black-potatoes-1704205681.jpg%