oreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fleopardtechlabs.com%2Fproducts%3Fcategory%3D6128b0b7f7a5e3ef8efe1703%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ewebsite%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20know%20more.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703859818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founders%20of%20Kerala-based%20Leopard%20Tech%20Labs%2C%20Allen%20Shaji%20and%20Sobin%20Matthew%20built%20the%20Hostile%20Activity%20Watch%20Kernel%20(HAWK)%20software%20to%20help%20forest%20departments%20fight%20wildlife%20crime.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20Aeroponic%20Towers%20Let%20You%20Grow%2030X%20More%20Vegetables%20in%20Small%20Balconies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Gupta%20has%20set%20up%20a%20kitchen%20garden%20to%20save%20his%20family%20from%20consuming%20pesticide-laden%20vegetables%20from%20the%20market.%20Recently%2C%20he%20included%20a%20unique%20aeroponic%20tower%20in%20his%20kitchen%20garden%20that%20grows%2032%20plants%20in%20an%20area%20that%20previously%20allowed%20the%20growth%20of%20only%20two%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20tower%20occupies%20as%20much%20space%20as%20a%20person%20takes%20while%20standing.%20And%20in%20this%20small%20space%2C%20I%20am%20growing%20several%20plants%20like%20ladyfingers%20and%20lettuce.%20I%20harvest%20lettuce%20for%20my%20salad%20every%20single%20day!%20Next%2C%20I%20am%20planning%20to%20grow%20bell%20peppers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abhishek%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20v